# Email Configuration for Contact Form
# Get Gmail App Password: https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/185833

# Gmail sender email (must be Gmail account)
EMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com

# Gmail App Password (NOT your regular password)
# Generate here: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your-app-password-here

# For production, add this to your hosting provider's environment variables
# Examples:
# - Vercel: Project Settings > Environment Variables
# - Netlify: Site settings > Build & deploy > Environment
# - AWS: Lambda environment variables or Secrets Manager

# Optional: Alternative Email Services
# For SendGrid, Mailgun, etc., modify lib/email.ts transporter config
